{"tid":1450990,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T00:30:56.000Z","uid":71480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"571825bc50ffc5bfe1f1b04c536b7a103df06ecf","tid":1450990,"uid":71480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:10:27.000Z","msg":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">統一口號</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">「黑警還眼」<br />\n<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」</div></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d4332b5fb833636766c95cc4f541bb0a49e8a1e6","tid":1450990,"uid":71480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:11:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gWTiArO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgWTiArO.jpg&h=83233e5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3d7a4eb411d2f968b1ba42e1e5db8daa36a0a33","tid":1450990,"uid":71480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pwKYArZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpwKYArZ.jpg&h=519fe5dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d13752527e23434481f16c80c0af41b0cf9f3ddb","tid":1450990,"uid":283668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:13:05.000Z","msg":"小編按：有醫護人員透露，指今晚眼部中槍的女生情況非常嚴重，現正準備進行緊急手術。有醫護人員與我們均認為人權組織需嚴正跟進事件，請各位替那位搶救中的女生祈禱。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/161014811328873/posts/489157275181290?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F161014811328873%2Fposts%2F489157275181290%3Fs